name: Chub Collins - Winners of the Ontario Tankard - 1903

desc.html:
Chub Collins, shown with the "Dundas Curling Club - Winners of the Ohio Tankard - 1903"
Dr. Lawson - Second, D. C. Wilson - Lead, Dr. T. A. Bertram - Skip, W. S. Hendry - Vice-Skip, H. C. Davis - Second, Jim Peare - Lead, H. F. Powell - Vice-Skip, Chub Collins - Skip.
